Method Detail

applyTo

public Expression applyTo(Expression e1,
                          Expression e2)
                   throws BinaryOperatorException
Applies the binary operator to the operands e1 and e2 and returns the resulting expression. If the operator cannot be applied to e1 and e2 because of a runtime type exception, a BinaryOperatorException is thrown.

Specified by:
applyTo in class BinaryOperator
Parameters:
e1 - the first operand.
e2 - the second operand.
Returns:
the resulting expression.
Throws:
BinaryOperatorException - if the operator cannot be applied to e1 and e2.
